oh yea he came home two days later<33
thank god<3

In this world of insanity and absurdity

Peace becomes an overwhelming feel

And goal to obtain.

 

The slightest touch of peace

Or sensation

Or feeling

Is one of the best

 

Lying on the ground

With specs of rain

Frozen into flakes

Of snow

In wintertime.

 

Bundled up like a marshmallow

Lying on the ground just resting

Listening to nothing

Has an effect

That affects the mind of the unexpected

 

The peace that is acquired by the snow fall

Is incredibly unobtainable by a callow mind,

Of most alive

And other flesh with no chance of ever experiencing

Such a feeling

Like that of peace.

 

But in an environment of white..

Quiet,

Experience,

Glow,

Sense,

And peace.

 

It becomes attainable.
